item.title: Being on a Careers Panel
item.description: As a University of Melbourne alumnus, I was invited to be on a careers panel on Open Day and share my experience as a software engineer with future students. During the discussion, students asked seemingly straightforward questions and yet I struggled to provide a replicable answer. Here’s why.
